prompts.frontCover: Greeting card front cover. Flat 2D botanical illustration of Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo, transformed into charming cartoon characters. They are standing in a lush, whimsical garden filled with oversized, fantastical plants. Lao Lao is depicted comically struggling to hold up an enormous, ridiculously heavy-looking potted plant, with a strained but laughing expression. Jordan stands beside her with a big, amused grin, playfully flexing one bicep as if offering useless help. The scene is framed by a beautiful archway of flowering vines like wisteria and trailing ivy. The background is a soft, solid pastel color. In the center, below the characters, is the text "Happy Birthday to my favorite weirdo" written in a beautiful, readable, handwritten cursive script. The style is lighthearted and humorous, with clean lines, soft textures, and a vibrant, natural color palette. --ar 4:5
